title: Week 15 Studs & Duds + Monday Punday, Full Tilt Hour - Fantasy Football Podcast for 12/20
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 15 weekend games! Which elite players lived up to expectations in the fantasy playoffs? Which duds will step it up in the next round? Plus, injury updates and Monday Punday! Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast. -- Fantasy Football Podcast for December 20th, 2021.
  
 (05:30) - Monday Punday
 (07:45) - NFL News 
 (16:40) - Fantasy Studmuffins
 (16:50) - QB Studs
 (25:15) - RB Studs
 (31:45) - WR Studs
 (34:05) - TE Studs
 (35:10) - Fantasy Duds
 (36:40) - QB Duds
 (39:20) - RB Duds
 (43:55) - WR Duds
 (46:35) - TE Duds
